projects.title: Attention Designers! Create an Exceptional Brand Style Guide for Oroshiuri Systems!
projects.description:
Are you a talented designer who can turn concepts into captivating visual assets? Do you possess a keen eye for detail and a passion for creating comprehensive brand guidelines? Look no further! Oroshiuri Systems is seeking a skilled freelancer like you to craft an outstanding Brand Style Guide using Canva.

About Oroshiuri Systems:
Oroshiuri Systems is a cutting-edge company dedicated to delivering innovative solutions in the field of technology. With our forward-thinking approach, we strive to revolutionize the industry and provide exceptional services to our clients. Our brand represents sophistication, reliability, and a commitment to excellence.

Project Requirements:
We have already designed our striking logo and collateral materials, but now we need a comprehensive Brand Style Guide to ensure consistent and cohesive branding across all touchpoints. The guide will serve as a valuable resource, demonstrating how to effectively use our logo, specifying our brand colors, font choices, and other essential elements typically found in a brand style guide.

Your Expertise:
As a skilled designer, you will leverage your creative flair and expertise in Canva to create an extraordinary Brand Style Guide that reflects Oroshiuri Systems' vision and values. Your responsibilities will include:

- Designing a visually appealing and user-friendly guide using Canva.
- Showcasing the proper usage of our logo in various contexts.
- Defining and presenting our primary and secondary brand colors.
- Selecting appropriate font choices for different applications.
- Incorporating graphic elements and visual guidelines.
- Outlining examples of correct and incorrect brand usage.
- Including any other essential components to ensure brand consistency.

Requirements:
To successfully undertake this project, you should possess the following qualifications:

- Proven experience in graphic design and creating brand style guides.
- Proficiency in Canva or similar design tools.
- A strong understanding of branding principles and design aesthetics.
- Excellent communication skills to collaborate effectively with our team.
- Attention to detail and the ability to meet project deadlines.

projects.title: 4 product dispensing unit
projects.description:
I'm constructing a dispensing unit with 4 tanks, 4 pumps, 4 hall effect liquid volume meters (pulse), and 4 solenoid valves. The tanks will each have an ultrasonic sensor that will need to be calibrated on my end to establish liquid level. the meters will also need to be calibrated as each of the chemicals being dispensed has a different specific gravity and commodities will change periodically.
The touch screen needs to display tank volumes on the home screen, a company logo background, and 4 buttons to select the commodity to be dispensed. The next screen will need to enable the operator to select an amount to be dispensed from 50 to 2000 ml and also display a graphic of the tank with available volume. unit should be programed to dispense only when an "execute" button is pressed on screen, then the operator will press an analog  button which will be mounted on the wand and should only dispense for a maximum of 30 seconds until an error " unable to dispense" message appears.

 I have an Arduino  Uno r3 and a stone 7" touchscreen with an 8 zone relay for the pumps and solenoids

Operator should be able to turn unit on, view tank levels, select item to be dispensed, set quantity, press "dispense", pick up the wand and aim and place it in the area to receive product, press the button on the wand and unit should engage the pump and solenoid until the required amount is dispensed, then remove the wand and replace it into its holder and dispense the next product.
